reviewText: How can I start? Those guys can move, The music was great. The lead singer did a wonderful job. His voice is so beautiful. Those guys gave a wonderful show. The oldies but goodies they sung brought back sweet memories. This is a very good DVD.
summary: I wont lend this one out!
Title: Stylistics, Stylistics - Live In Norfolk 2005

reviewText: Good show from a truly legendary R&B group. The audio was okay however the video leaves much to be desired. I must have concert for any fan of the Stylistics.
Title: Stylistics, Stylistics - Live In Norfolk 2005

reviewText: If you like the Stylistics, you'll love this DVD.  Great price too.  Most of their hits are included and they do a great job.
Title: Stylistics, Stylistics - Live In Norfolk 2005

reviewText: The Stylistics were loved by everyone and still are.  They were so very smooth and their performances just solidifies that.
Title: Stylistics, Stylistics - Live In Norfolk 2005

reviewText: A great DVD from one of the all time great Soul groups. A deinite keeper and one for all to have in their collection.
Title: Stylistics, Stylistics - Live In Norfolk 2005
